you're gonna see a lot more.

01:39.233 --> 01:41.100
You're gonna
appreciate nature way more,

01:41.168 --> 01:44.970
and honestly, it's
gonna take you further.

01:46.306 --> 01:48.240
And not knowing what's ahead,

01:48.308 --> 01:50.559
not knowing what's
around that next corner?

