I'm essentially gearing up for

02:40.761 --> 02:44.629
the most important
hunt of the year.

02:44.632 --> 02:46.364
This is a hunt
that you put up, uh,

02:46.367 --> 02:48.633
enough food to last you months,

02:48.636 --> 02:51.970
to get you by when no
other game animals are around.

02:51.972 --> 02:54.239
That's what's going to kind
of make or break my winter.

02:54.241 --> 02:56.308
Aside from the ice
this beach is great.

02:56.310 --> 02:59.044
Essentially this is what
you call winter's knocking

02:59.112 --> 03:00.512
at the door right here.

03:00.581 --> 03:02.380
You know, it's gonna
hinder me from hunting,

03:02.383 --> 03:03.782
it's going to
hinder me from fishing,

03:03.784 --> 03:05.317
