this fall fishing time to meet

04:50.824 --> 04:52.224
our needs throughout the year.

04:53.577 --> 04:56.161
All right guys, we found a
good spot to put the net, I think.

04:57.698 --> 04:59.164
Ryder I'm gonna
need your help, okay?

04:59.166 --> 05:00.565
RYDER: Okay.

05:00.567 --> 05:02.367
