good spot to tie up the net.

05:04.638 --> 05:07.038
Looks like a great spot.

05:07.041 --> 05:08.440
Come on out.

05:09.242 --> 05:11.509
One of our big responsibilities
is teaching our children

05:11.512 --> 05:13.511
