05:13.514 --> 05:14.579
Awesome, come on out.

05:14.581 --> 05:15.781
You got it?

05:15.849 --> 05:17.182
Way to go, buddy.

05:17.250 --> 05:19.951
Okay now go ahead and wrap
this around that tree two times.

05:21.322 --> 05:23.121
RYDER: Oh, I got it.
SONTA: Okay, cool.

05:23.123 --> 05:26.191
