the generation that stops that.

05:28.729 --> 05:31.596
Pull it against
the tree, there you go.

05:31.598 --> 05:32.864
Mm-hmm.

05:32.933 --> 05:35.934
We want our kids to
take ownership of fishing.

05:36.002 --> 05:38.003
There we go, ready
to go set this net?

05:38.071 --> 05:40.138
RYDER: I think it's good.
SONTA: Okay, let's jump in.

05:40.407 --> 05:42.741
