06:17.110 --> 06:19.844
It's not going into an
S-curve or anything like that.

06:19.847 --> 06:22.647
CHEVIE: How does it look, Sonta?
SONTA: Hey, Chev, we're good!

06:22.716 --> 06:24.115
Good job, guys.

06:24.118 --> 06:25.817
SYDNEY: Good job, yay!
RYDER: Yeah, that was good.

06:25.853 --> 06:27.319
SONTA: We'll see
what we get here.

